messages.body: $AGIO This price action reminds me of AIMT just before they were bought. links.description: CAMBRIDGE, Mass., Sept. 21, 2020 -- Agios Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (NASDAQ: AGIO), a leader in the field of cellular metabolism to treat cancer and rare genetic diseases, today announced the results of the final overall survival (OS) analysis from its global Phase 3 ClarIDHy trial of TIBSOVO(R) (ivosidenib tablets) in previously treated cholangiocarcinoma patients with an isocitrate dehydrogenase 1 (IDH1) mutation.
